{"tid":253863,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 懷疑生智慧齒","createTime":"2017-05-22T17:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T01:13:11.000Z","uid":108951,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4838c34b438d97f407cfa877faa1f6e3baa61d8","tid":253863,"uid":108951,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:34:59.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜開始覺得牙肉腫腫地，又有d痛，一開始諗住係自己夜訓，可能熱氣先牙肉腫。<br />\n但係愈來愈嚴重，而家食野咬野都好痛，個位置係下個個把牙齒右邊最入既位置。<br />\n剛剛去摸下佢，結果摸到少少牙齒咁，有一角仔。牙肉入面都有個硬塊，我諗係隻牙黎既。<br />\n我想問我而家可以點，係咪要睇醫生？定係要等隻牙生出黎先去睇？<br />\n另外想問下有無好既牙醫介紹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7bd08b776e7eb497ee78f8703d8347f66e05a6","tid":253863,"uid":101367,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:36:11.000Z","msg":"由佢生出黎，點解要睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f2292aedf2ce2c8fa4e970f34bb5dae00b73c6","tid":253863,"uid":108951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:37:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由佢生出黎，點解要睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食飯都咬唔落野"},{"pid":"04ee581d5ae641a46848c8a2cf26cbacd08fa06d","tid":253863,"uid":25340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想屌樓主 中學雞？<br />\n如果你怕咪去睇下牙醫 可能一早生緊你唔知 而你平時又冇理佢令到佢收埋左d污糟野"},{"pid":"794c34b2738ae0a58d73ba2ef85067eab15050b8","tid":253863,"uid":98042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T18:00:43.000Z","msg":"屌 same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im